- **Aesthetic Enhancements:** Evaluate the visual appeal of pages, ensuring the design language aligns with FFPMA’s brand standards, which emphasize deep blues, teals, cyan, and gold. Ensure motifs of DNA helixes and healing frequencies are subtly integrated.


- **Interactive Flows:** Assess ease of navigation and the intuitiveness of interactive elements. Aim to simplify user paths, reduce friction, and enhance member engagement by ensuring interactions reflect a journey towards wellness education and personal sovereignty.


- **Modern Design Principles:** Implement responsive design, reduce page load times, and ensure accessibility standards are met. Consider adding animations and microinteractions that provide feedback and guide users gently yet effectively.


## Proposed Enhancements


### Landing Page (`client/src/pages/landing.tsx`)


- **Hero Section Redesign:**
