  - Update call-to-action buttons to be more prominent using gold accents for enlightenment, drawing users toward wellness education and protocols.


- **Visual Consistency:**
  - Unify iconography across the page with motifs of healing frequencies, ensuring that each visual element serves to enhance user understanding and retention.


- **Content Layout:**
  - Increase white space utilization to improve readability and focus, particularly around key mission statements and core values.


- **Performance Optimization:**
  - Implement lazy loading for images and deferred loading techniques for non-critical JavaScript to improve initial load time.


### Member Dashboard (`client/src/pages/member-dashboard.tsx`)


- **User Path Simplification:**
  - Reorganize the dashboard layout to prioritize access to personalized wellness protocols and an easy view of recently accessed resources.


- **Interactive Elements:**
